{
  "stem": "1901.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Ampfing, it was in very bad lager, and they were carrying bags of cement.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the main work there-- up to-- up a hill, this up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And no one made it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They say one, two, three days, they were gone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was terrible there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I never made it, because the next day, I don't know what commander want to give us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The next day there was-- oh, I tell you that, the-- he bombs were throwing around left and right.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was an enormous attack from the Americans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In Muhldorf is a railway crossing, apparently.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the whole-- the whole camp had to go to Muhldorf railway crossing to clean the rails and the wagons.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that took weeks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, every day there, and-- and picking up what was there, and shifting, and you know-- make the roads clear for-- for that the train could run again, roll again.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it took a week, what it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we cleaned it up nicely.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We didn't do it too fast.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I even found an American in-- I remember when we walked to the railway station, we found an American body in-- that was a shot from a plane.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we found a whole American.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we took his cigarettes, and his belt, and what-- and what we could get from him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I mean, there was no feeling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was dead.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I had a little bit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I had a few pack of cigarettes, and could deal with it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You could deal with the outside, you know, even with-- I must say, the SS start disappearing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It became home guards, old men.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They were also SS, or Wehrmacht.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they were just as frightened as we were, really.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
